procedure cpro003a
*listado de padrones con padron creado
* nuevo diseĊo alfabtico total, sin titulos
set talk off
set delete on
set printer off
set device to screen
@04,01 clear to 23,78
@04,28 say 'LISTADO DE PADRONES     '
close all
select 2
use PADRON
SORT to padrons on   padayn
do imprime
@04,01 clear to 23,78
